title: Are You Ready For This Belly? See All of Beyoncé’s Pregnancy Pics (PHOTOS)
text:
Beyoncé saved surprised the world when she announced she’s expecting twins with husband Jay Z on Wednesday, February 1. 
To celebrate the exciting news, Queen Bey posted a series of intimate and interesting pregnancy photos to her website. Click through the gallery above to see them all!
